# 🚀 Coding Profile Analyzer

A full-stack **Developer Analytics Dashboard** that fetches and visualizes coding profiles from multiple platforms like Codeforces, LeetCode, GitHub, HackerRank, and LinkedIn.

---

## 🔥 Features

* 🔍 Search any username across platforms
* 🌐 Multi-platform support

  * Codeforces
  * LeetCode
  * GitHub
  * HackerRank (basic)
  * LinkedIn (profile link)
* 📊 Interactive charts (difficulty distribution)
* 📈 Contest history graph (Codeforces)
* 🔥 GitHub contribution heatmap
* 🏆 Compare users (coming soon)
* 🎨 Modern UI with Tailwind CSS
* ⚡ Fast and responsive

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

### Frontend

* React JS
* Tailwind CSS
* Recharts

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* Axios

---

