---

## ⚙️ Installation

### 1️⃣ Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/coding-profile-analyzer.git
cd coding-profile-analyzer
```

---

### 2️⃣ Setup Backend

```bash
cd server
npm install
npm run dev
```

Server runs on:

```
http://localhost:5000
```

---

### 3️⃣ Setup Frontend

```bash
cd client
npm install
npm run dev
```

Frontend runs on:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

---

## 🔌 API Endpoints

| Platform   | Endpoint                |
| ---------- | ----------------------- |
| Codeforces | `/codeforces/:username` |
| LeetCode   | `/leetcode` (POST)      |
| GitHub     | `/github` (POST)        |
| HackerRank | `/hackerrank/:username` |
| LinkedIn   | `/linkedin` (POST)      |

---

## 📊 Features Explained

### 📌 Codeforces

* Rating
* Rank
* Contest data

### 📌 LeetCode

* Total solved
* Easy / Medium / Hard breakdown

### 📌 GitHub

* Profile data
* Contributions (heatmap)

### 📌 HackerRank

* Basic stats (scraping planned)

### 📌 LinkedIn

* Direct profile link

